Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be another hot day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot when you wear\Nso many clothes during the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Isn't it the newspaper\Nfrom three days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's a couple from Verden?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They said the murderer was a doctor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you're\Ngoing to Verden too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if I'll get to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,GIESSEN POLICE STATION\N(GERMANY)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in the French Foreign Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After you became a mercenary,\Nyou joined the 1979 Nicaraguan Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1981 to 1984,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you aided the anti-government\Nguerrillas in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1987, you played an important role\Nin Mossad's secret assassination campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,against a radical Islamist faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quite an extensive combat history,\NMr. Hugo Bernhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As the seminar was held by an excellent\Nmercenary like yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume the graduating students\Nwere excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like our young officers\Nto attend your class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so they could be retrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, there's no need…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this man an outstanding student\Nas well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he came to your training center\Naround five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a genius with a scalpel in his hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but was he great with a gun as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,FIVE MONTHS EARLIER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you taught how to shoot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-So you're self-taught?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never fired a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Not even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that it's an absurd request,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are the only one I can turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, now that you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to forget everything\Nyou know about guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never taught anyone\Nwho has never fired a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jump rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're experienced or not,\Nwe always start with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't just stand there!\N-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Start now.\N-Ye… Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Much faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to jump as well as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always supervise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the training for the instructor like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll do it, so you can stop\Nstaring at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's looking\Nfor food for her chicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you too tired to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating is part of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she… your daughter?\NOr your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot and killed that child's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it right in front of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in Myanmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went into a hut in the jungle\Nto hide, I found them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother had a gun pointing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was a second later,\Nshe would've shot me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought the girl\Nhere with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since she started living with me,\Nshe has never laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,hate me for the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what will happen\Nwhen you use a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want that, never hold one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells nice.\NI think it smells like daphne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After running,\Ncome to the low ground behind the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The low ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Firing range…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully. Two shots consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you shoot,\Nalways pull the trigger twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your chance of killing someone will rise\Ndramatically by shooting twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,consider yourself dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You always cook for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I would make\NJapanese food for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called nikujaga.\NI hope you will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chopsticks.\NI pared down some wood to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be more Japanese\Nif we use these to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at using chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a baby brambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have fallen from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't.\NWe have to return it to its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be hard to raise the bird\Naway from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They rarely ever survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return it to its nest,\Nback to its mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds. Everything will be\Ndecided in three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you miss or hesitate\Nfor even a split second,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who will be shot\Nand killed is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was the grade
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the man graduated with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He got a perfect score on his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He reached\Nthe necessary level of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Overall, his concentration was superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be another story for him\Nto actually kill a person with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he can shoot someone\Nfor the first time or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where the path diverges.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It will decide whether he can\Nuse a gun or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Which do you think he will take?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you know where he's headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,\NI would appreciate it if you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for the past five months."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Here's the payment for the rest\Nof the training."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Also, please have the nikujaga."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it?\NDo you know where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
